**Long live the king! Survive the battles and ambushes, keep the king alive!**

Controls (Keyboard + Mouse):

â- Escape - Restart battle;
- Scroll Mouse Wheel - Camera Zoom In/Out;
- Hold Mouse Wheel Button and Drag  -  Drag Camera;
- Click with Left Mouse Button on a player squad, Drag to prepare movement direction and Release the button move the squad:
![LD46 image2.png](///raw/0dd/2/z/2c132.png)

*Win Conditions:*
- King captured the flag;
- All AI squads defeated.

*Lose Conditions:*
- King is defeated;
- All player squads defeated.

DITAZURE is an arcade game;

You wake up in deep darkness, kinda nowhere, surrounded by the voices;

Your only hope is power core which is slowly discharging;

You need to power it up, but how?;

Wait...., I think I see someone....

Oh sh***t;


Try to survive as long as you can and share your score; 


![cover.png](///raw/c51/51/z/2c052.png)

I've made this game for Compo, fortunately made it on time (like in half time);

Technical info:
-Made with Unity Engine
-Sprites and Animations were done in Aseprite
-Music and SFX were made in FL Studio 20
-Coding made in Visual Studio (hate this tho)

All things weer made by myself during this Ludum Dare;
Even this voices and distorted background music, I've recorded it by myself, yesterday (19.04) at 7 am;

A dark Top-down Beat-em-up in purgatory. Earn an impressive combo to convince your lords to redeem your soul.
Code, graphics, audio and music done solo within 48 hours for the Ludum Dare 46 Compo.


CONTROLS:
Arrows - move; 
X - dodge; 
C - attack; 
V - disperse; 

![coverimage2.png](///raw/dbe/91/z/2ba97.png)

